STATE EX REL. DUDAS
v.
LUCCI 2019-0537 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 21, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On respondent's motion to dismiss. Motion denied. Sua sponte, cause dismissed for failure to state a claim in prohibition. Relator's motion to strike respondent's motion to dismiss denied as moot. Respondent's motion for leave to amend motion to dismiss denied as moot. O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and Stewart, JJ., concur. Donnelly, J., not participating.
